      { kind: "list", items: ["Collection — your full music library. Import, analyse, organise. Source: rekordbox Manual — Collection window p.7", "EXPORT mode — prepare USB drives with analysed tracks and playlists for club CDJs. Source: rekordbox Manual — EXPORT mode p.48", "PERFORMANCE mode — use rekordbox itself as playback software with a controller. Source: rekordbox Manual — PERFORMANCE mode p.104", "Analysis — auto-detects BPM, key, waveform, beat grid for every track. Source: rekordbox Manual — Analysis p.14", "PRO DJ LINK — network connection between rekordbox and CDJ hardware. Source: rekordbox Manual p.67"] },
      { kind: "callout", tone: "key", text: "rekordbox has two essential modes: EXPORT (prepare your USB for club CDJs) and PERFORMANCE (use rekordbox with a controller). Understand both. Source: rekordbox Manual p.6" }
